						               													<description>Find It &amp;amp; Bind It is a card game for 2-6 people that runs roughly 10 mins/player.  Each player controls 2 witches that are searching through a 3x3 field of Book Cards for The Book of Shadows.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Spell Cards are used to Scry (look at) and/or Obfuscate (look at &amp;amp; move) the Book Cards around and interact with other players to thwart their progress.  To win, you must find The Book of Shadows, get both of your witches to it and then use your action to bind it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With one real Book of Shadows in a sea of fakes, can your sisters be the ones to Find It &amp;amp; Bind It first in this game of spell casting and an ever-changing landscape?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
